        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="work" decls="#md" met="E">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <bibl source="digital">Michela Naccari</bibl>
                </head>
                <div2 xml:id="001c001" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>1</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l1" n="tit.">1. Ad Molsam parantem D. Augusti Sepulcrum | Instaurare</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l2" n="1">Haud dubium est vates quondam fovisse benigne</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l3" n="2">Augustum, vates non minor ille suis.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l4" n="3">Nemo tamen maiora tulit, nec istius uno</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l5" n="4">Virgilio, docet hoc Principis ingenium.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l6" n="5">Praeterea est semper Musas veneratus in armis,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l7" n="6">Ipsa suum tenuit Calliopea locum.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l8" n="7">Quid mirum est igitur quod tu divine Poeta,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l9" n="8">In quo Virgilii mens micat, atque animus,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l10" n="9">Tam pius Augusti reparas monumenta, et honori</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l11" n="10">Vis redeant prisco diruta busta Dei.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l12" n="11">Maxima laus haec, et solum te digna, decebat</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l13" n="12">Te servare istis unice Molsa sacris.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l14" n="13">Maxima laus haec est, tumulum pietate reponi,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l15" n="14">Non alia credas, quam voluisse tua.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l16" n="15">Hippolytus iam Molsa tuus cum Caesare gaudet,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l17" n="16">Tertius ingeminat verba secunda Maro.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l18" n="17">Felices umbrae, mo... at felicior es tu,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l19" n="18">Per quem sanct..... restituetur honor.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c002" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>2</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l20" n="tit.">2. Al Sig. Molza mio fratello amatissimo</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l21" n="1">Nymphae, quae virides saltus, quaeque abdita Pindi</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l22" n="2">Humano colitis non adeunda pede;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l23" n="3">Ne vos ne pigeat densis discedere ab umbris,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l24" n="4">Antraque muscoso liquere picta solo,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l25" n="5">Laetifer immiti quamvis nunc lumine passim</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l26" n="6">Contristet duros Syrius agricolas</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l27" n="7">Molza meus vestros coluit qui semper honores,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l28" n="8">Cuique dedit sacros Phoebus inire choros,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l29" n="9">Iamdudum graciles morbo tenuatus in artus,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l30" n="10">Extremam in mortis limine poscit opem.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l31" n="11">Ergo herbas, succosque simul afferte salubres,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l32" n="12">Et medicae quicquid Cynthius artis habet.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l33" n="13">Non levis exiguis aderit nam gloria factis,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l34" n="14">Vos uno incolumi restituisse duos.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c003" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>3</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l35" n="">3.</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l36" n="1">Flagro, paene nefas, sed flagro cupidine vitae</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l37" n="2">Post mea ducendae tristia fata diu.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l38" n="3">Despondenti animum, proprio id mihi Marte licere,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l39" n="4">Viribus ingenii Molsa favere potes.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l40" n="5">Aera parent alii, quaerantque hi vivere in auro,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l41" n="6">Longaevosque illos sculptile marmor agat.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l42" n="7">Dum scriptis me utcunque suis tua Musa reponat,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l43" n="8">Tu mihi Praxiteles, tu mihi Mentor eris.</l>
                </div2>
            </div1>
